The paper discusses the theory and applications of submodular functions in machine learning, which involves optimization, algorithms, and data structures. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
